      <section eId="sec_45_24_4">
        <num>45-24-4</num>
        <content>
          <p>From and after July 1, 1997, no employer shall cause the involuntary separation of a state officer or employee without the prior approval of the commission. An employer may proceed with a reorganization which might result in such involuntary separation without prior approval of the commission upon compliance with Code Section 45-24-8.</p>
